GreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1020409, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah (I begin), in Allah (I trust), and the course of Allah’s Messenger (I follow), peace be upon him and his Household. I bear witness that there is no god save Allah, One and Only God and having no partner. And I bear witness that Muhammad is His servant and Messenger and I bear witness that the commander of faithful and the leader of pious Ali is Allah’s most intimate servant.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Khuda ke naam se Khuda ki zaat ke waaste se aur Rasool-e-Khuda (s.a.w.a) ke tareeqe par Khuda rehmat kare un par aur unki Aal (a.s) par. Mai gawahi deta hu keh Allah ke siwa koi ma’bood nahi jo yakta hai, koi uska shareek nahi. Mai gawahi deta hu keh Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) Uske bande aur Rasool aur mai gawahi deta hu keh momeeno ke Amir aur muttaqiyo’n ke Imam Hazrat Ali (a.s) Khuda ke Wali hai.", "Urdu": "خدا کے نام سے خدا کی ذات کے واسطے سے اور رسولؐ خدا کے طریقے پر خدا رحمت کرے ان پر اور ان کی آلؑ پر میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ اللہ کے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں جو یکتا ہے کوئی اس کا شریک نہیں میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ حضرت محمد ؐاس کے بندے اور رسولؐ ہیں اور میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ مومنوں کے امیر اور متقیوں کے امام حضرت علیؑ خدا کے ولی ہیں۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHE WA BILLAAHE WA FEE SABEE-LIL-LAAHE WA A'LAA MILLA-TE RASOOLIL-LAAHE SALLALLAAHO A'LAYHE WA AALEHI, ASH-HADO AN LAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO WAHDA-HU LAA SHAREE-KA LAHU WA ASH-HADO ANNA MOHAMMADAN A'BDO-HU WA RASOOLO-HU WA ASH-HADO ANNA AMEE-RAL MOMENEENA WA IMAA-MAL MUTTA-QEENA A'LIYYAN WALIYYULLAAH.", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ وَبِاللہِ وَفِیْ سَبِیْلِ اللہِ وَعَلٰی مِلَّۃِ رَسُوْلِ اللہِ صَلَّی اللہُ عَلَیْہِ وَاٰلِہٖ۔ اَشْہَدُ اَنْ لَّا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ وَحْدَہٗ لَا شَرِیْکَ لَہٗ وَاَشْہَدُ اَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُہٗ وَرَسُوْلُہٗ وَاَشْہَدُ اَنَّ اَمِیْرَ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ وَاِمَامَ الْمُتَّقِیْنَ عَلِیًّا وَّلِیُّ اللہِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRed